# Cursor AI Rules for Project Tutwiler

## How to Start the Application

### Windows
Run `start.bat` or `startup-wizard.ps1` - This opens a GUI wizard that handles everything.

### Mac/Linux  
Run `./setup.sh` then `./start.sh` - Command-line setup and start.

## Key Information

- This is a Docker Compose microservices application
- All services run in containers
- `.env` file is created from `.env.backup` template
- Frontend: http://localhost:3000
- Admin: http://localhost:3000/admin/analytics

## Demo Access
- `DEMO_LOGIN_VERIFIED` - Verified dashboard
- `DEMO_LOGIN_NON_VERIFIED` - Non-verified dashboard
- `DEMO_LOGIN_ADMIN` - Admin dashboard

## When Making Changes
- Frontend: Restart with `docker-compose restart frontend`
- Backend: Rebuild with `docker-compose build [service] && docker-compose up -d [service]`
- Always check logs: `docker-compose logs [service]`

